================== kr 2.x.x ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS ===================================

kr 2.x.x [1] computes a distance matrix between genomes based on Kr, 
the estimator of the rate of substitution [2]. 

kr 2.x.x code contributors:
	Mirjana Domazet-Lošo
	Bernhard Haubold

References:
[1] Domazet-Lošo, M., and Haubold, B. 2009.
    Efficient Efficient Estimation of Pairwise Distances between Genomes
    (submitted)
  
[2] Haubold, B., Pfaffelhuber, P., Domazet-Lošo, M., and Wiehe, T. 2009. 
    Estimating mutation distances from unaligned genomes, J. Comput. Biol.
    (in press)
